settings.description: Honestly loosely based on one level from the SMBX game 'the invasion 2', for remember a level with the hammer bros themes and mario bros elements? well... here I'm trying to go for that theme!
La vitesse court trop vite c'est un niveau que Sherigeok Doit jouer.
Well, the objective is stupidly simple. Find the right level and don't do all that hard work for nothing! P-Wing included for special time wasting! Careful as something may block your path.
This level has 5 ace coins and it has 250 sseconds, you need to defeat ludwig to end the level.
